cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.SY, cs.CR 

This paper discusses the impact of network densification on wireless networks, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication technologies. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses the propagation of signals and interference management, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the challenges of applying interference management, which is related to systems and control (cs.SY) and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
